Wellington Phoenix Team News

Wellington Phoenix FC were founded in March 2007, with the team known as The Nix or Yellow Army, with the home ground being the Sky Stadium. This football club always aim to be competitive in the A-League, with the upcoming fixtures being published at Sportsgambler.com when the list has been announced. You can also see the latest results, with lineup information being available in a predicted and confirmed basis.
